main event: On July 8, 1964, multiple witnesses reported seeing unidentified flying objects in the sky over Clearwater, Florida.
interesting points: The sightings included objects described as bright, round, and emitting a white glow,Many witnesses reported witnessing strange lights in the sky on July 4th, causing confusion,Police Chief Dempsey Barron stated that the lights did not resemble any known aircraft,An investigation was conducted by Project Blue Book, several documents were generated about the sightings, many witnesses corroborated the events they observed.
sighted object: Unidentified flying objects, including bright lights and round objects
witness description: Multiple residents and officials including police and civillians stating they observed strange flying lights or objects.
